ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectWheat, amber durum wheat & designated barley - 2008-2009 INTERIM PAYMENT February 1, 2008 to July 31, 2009 INTERIM PAYMENT
PrecisOrder authorizing and directing THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to make an INTERIM PAYMENT to producers for the WHEAT, AMBER DURUM WHEAT and DESIGNATED BARLEY pool accounts for the pool period commencing on August 1, 2008 and terminating on July 31, 2009.
